    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Search of the Golden Crops</strong> is a cozy experience focused on the joy of planting and harvesting. Manage your resources, use strategy with card packs, and watch your farm grow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Harvest</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click to harvest your crops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/c925fd425ede7c7524856d07b9c51526.poster.avif?t=1769558853\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/c925fd425ede7c7524856d07b9c51526.webm?t=1769558853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/c925fd425ede7c7524856d07b9c51526.mp4?t=1769558853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your farm to improve your crops</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/e88251207cfeaa41d731c39185e1a081.poster.avif?t=1769558853\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/e88251207cfeaa41d731c39185e1a081.webm?t=1769558853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/e88251207cfeaa41d731c39185e1a081.mp4?t=1769558853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Task board</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete tasks from the Task Board.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/14626298320bfc56cd6c49d2a68a3204.poster.avif?t=1769558853\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/14626298320bfc56cd6c49d2a68a3204.webm?t=1769558853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/14626298320bfc56cd6c49d2a68a3204.mp4?t=1769558853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Store</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy new card packs at the Store</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/14c16981e06b60b07144fe243a48a7dc.poster.avif?t=1769558853\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/14c16981e06b60b07144fe243a48a7dc.webm?t=1769558853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Market</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell your crops at the Market</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/611d503ad920decc0d1cdb7e22fe11e0.poster.avif?t=1769558853\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/611d503ad920decc0d1cdb7e22fe11e0.webm?t=1769558853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270970/extras/611d503ad920decc0d1cdb7e22fe11e0.mp4?t=1769558853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"b